"title": "7155: saints",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7155",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The people of God, especially in relation to their being set apart from the world to serve him. Believers are called upon to lead holy lives worthy of their calling.</p>\n<h2>Saints are set apart for God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:2\">1CO 1:2</a></strong> <em>To be holy is to be set apart.  The same Greek word is used in the NT for both “holy” and, in the plural, “saints”.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">DEU 7:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:19\">DEU 26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:3\">PSA 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:7\">ROM 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:10\">HEB 10:10</a></p>\n<h3>They are members of God's covenant people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:8\">PSA 85:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:41\">2CH 6:41</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:9\">PSA 132:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:4\">PSA 30:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:9\">PSA 34:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:5\">PSA 50:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:1-Ps79:2\">PSA 79:1–79:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:16\">PSA 132:16</a></p>\n<h3>They are believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:15\">ROM 16:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:27\">ROM 8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:31\">ROM 15:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:21-Phil4:22\">PHP 4:21–4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:26\">COL 1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:10\">1TI 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>They make up the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:33\">1CO 14:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:32\">ACT 9:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:1\">EPH 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:2\">COL 1:2</a></p>\n<h2>Saints are to live lives worthy of their calling</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3-Eph5:4\">EPH 5:3–5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:2\">ROM 16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1-Eph4:3\">EPH 4:1–4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:11\">2PE 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:10\">REV 13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:12\">REV 14:12</a></p>\n<h2>Saints have responsibility for one another</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:13\">ROM 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:25-Rom15:26\">ROM 15:25–15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:1\">1CO 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:1-1Cor16:2\">1CO 16:1–16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:15\">1CO 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:1-2Cor9:2\">2CO 9:1–9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:12\">2CO 9:12</a></p>\n<h2>Saints have spiritual union with Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:11\">HEB 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:4-John15:5\">JHN 15:4–15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:2\">1CO 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:1\">EPH 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:1\">PHP 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:21\">PHP 4:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:2\">COL 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:10\">2TH 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>Saints may be persecuted</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:19\">JHN 15:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:21\">DAN 7:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:25\">DAN 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:24\">DAN 8:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:14\">JHN 17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:13\">ACT 9:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:10\">ACT 26:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:7\">REV 13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:6\">REV 16:6</a></p>\n<h2>Saints are precious in God's sight</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:3\">PSA 16:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:15\">PSA 116:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:11\">PSA 147:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:4\">PSA 149:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18\">EPH 1:18</a></p>\n<h3>They enjoy God's protection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:9\">1SA 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:23\">PSA 31:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:28\">PSA 37:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:10\">PSA 97:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:8\">PRO 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>They experience exaltation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:18\">DAN 7:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:6-Ps149:9\">PSA 149:6–149:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:22\">DAN 7:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:27\">DAN 7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:52\">MAT 27:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:2\">1CO 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12\">COL 1:12</a></p>",
